---
// Module 2: What is Silicon Age
---

<section class="section" id="concept">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="concept-grid">
      <!-- Left: text -->
      <div class="concept-text">
        <div class="section-tag animate-on-scroll">Core Concept</div>
        <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll">What is the Silicon Age?</h2>
        <p class="concept-lead animate-on-scroll">
          The Silicon Age is more than a leap in computing power. It is the full evolution of information technology — from perception to cognition to decision-making — extending human intelligence onto silicon chips.
        </p>
        <p class="concept-body animate-on-scroll">
          It marks the moment when algorithms cease to be abstract tools and become active participants in the physical world. Computation, intelligence, and reality converge into a single fabric — amplifying human capability, creativity, and reach.
        </p>

        <!-- Data tags -->
        <div class="concept-tags animate-on-scroll">
          <span class="data-tag">PERCEPTION → COGNITION → ACTION</span>
          <span class="data-tag">HUMAN + MACHINE</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Featured image -->
        <div class="concept-image animate-on-scroll">
          <img src="/images/ai-brain.jpg" alt="AI and human intelligence convergence" />
          <span class="image-label mono-label">PLANET-SCALE INTELLIGENCE</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: visual card -->
      <div class="concept-visual animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="glass-card ar-card ar-card-extra concept-card">
          <span class="corner-tr"></span>
          <span class="corner-bl"></span>

          <div class="card-diagram">
            <div class="diagram-layer">
              <span class="layer-num">01</span>
              <span class="layer-name">Perception</span>
              <span class="layer-desc">Sensors, data, understanding</span>
            </div>
            <div class="diagram-arrow">↓</div>
            <div class="diagram-layer">
              <span class="layer-num">02</span>
              <span class="layer-name">Cognition</span>
              <span class="layer-desc">Analysis, learning, insight</span>
            </div>
            <div class="diagram-arrow">↓</div>
            <div class="diagram-layer">
              <span class="layer-num">03</span>
              <span class="layer-name">Decision</span>
              <span class="layer-desc">Action, impact, feedback</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card-footer-label mono-label">INTELLIGENCE PIPELINE // ACTIVE</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .concept-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .concept-lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .concept-body {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .concept-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .data-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--cyan);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--cyan-dim);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.03);
  }

  .concept-card { padding: 2rem; }

  .card-diagram {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .diagram-layer {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 32px 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: 0 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.015);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .layer-num {
    grid-row: 1 / 3;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--magenta);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .layer-name {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .layer-desc {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .diagram-arrow {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .card-footer-label {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    text-align: right;
  }

  .concept-image {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    position: relative;
  }

  .concept-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 180px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    filter: brightness(0.85) saturate(0.85);
    transition: filter 0.3s;
  }

  .concept-image:hover img {
    filter: brightness(1) saturate(1);
  }

  .concept-image .image-label {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0.75rem;
    right: 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(10, 12, 18, 0.8);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .concept-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
